{"tid":212544,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(螺絲cover) 陳奕迅 - K歌之王","createTime":"2017-04-22T13:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T08:20:47.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76586f60980577d88770e2865869d784585ceef4","tid":212544,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"我終於成為連登仔, 加入連登音樂台呢個大家庭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟視唱歌為生命之一, 當時唔少得幾首cover啦!<br />\n我就比大家聽下我至愛嘅K歌之王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DQLxGdw9Elo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDQLxGdw9Elo&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=eb1b4efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DQLxGdw9Elo</a><br />\n我唱得不夠動人你別皺眉<br />\n我願意和你約定至死<br />\n我只想嬉戲唱遊到下世紀<br />\n請你別嫌我將這煽情奉獻給你<br />\n<br />\n還能憑甚麼 擁抱若未能令你興奮<br />\n便宜地唱出 寫在情歌的性感<br />\n還能憑甚麼 要是愛不可感動人<br />\n俗套的歌詞 煽動你惻忍<br />\n<br />\n誰人又相信一世一生這膚淺對白<br />\n來吧送給你叫幾百萬人流淚過的歌<br />\n如從未聽過誓言如幸福摩天輪<br />\n才令我因你要呼天叫地愛愛愛愛那麼多<br />\n<br />\n將我漫天心血一一拋到銀河<br />\n誰是垃圾 誰不捨我難過 分一丁目贈我<br />\n<br />\n我唱出心裡話時眼淚會流<br />\n要是怕難過抱住我手<br />\n我只得千語萬言放在你心<br />\n比渴望地老天荒更簡單未算罕有<br />\n<br />\n誰人又相信一世一生這膚淺對白<br />\n來吧送給你叫幾百萬人流淚過的歌<br />\n如從未聽過誓言如幸福摩天輪<br />\n才令我因你要呼天叫地愛愛愛愛那麼多<br />\n<br />\n給你用力作二十首不捨不棄<br />\n還附送你愛得過火<br />\n給你賣力唱二十首真心真意<br />\n麥克風都因我動容 無人及我<br />\n你怎麼竟然說K歌之王 是我<br />\n<br />\n我只想跟你未來浸在愛河<br />\n而你那呵欠絕得不能絕 絕到溶掉我<br />\n<br />\n請留評語, 唱得唔好即管負皮<br />\n另外歡迎各位subscibe我嘅youtube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (不過為左方便大家聽歌, 我都係會不定時upload cover)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCggnb8BbKlpbycpANg2ZFbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCggnb8BbKlpbycpANg2ZFbg&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7863e024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCggnb8BbKlpbycpANg2ZFbg</a>"},{"pid":"a1b6197b0e39dd16c5b8955794c492cda085fe6c","tid":212544,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"YouTube 乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cab3249cc2a5e69fd9fd3fd8fa1932b4ffd0920","tid":212544,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"宣傳宣傳者, 岩岩新到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b52141648ba865749f66df56a0e7c02e34682ed","tid":212544,"uid":30123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30e6a7f3e603c41a25d6e51331fee99ff403abc","tid":212544,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宣傳宣傳者, 岩岩新到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正正經經打份工啦<br />\n<br />\n乞兒"},{"pid":"1d7f6276c3be6658461f51d3883ff33f3441afe1","tid":212544,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"讀緊書"},{"pid":"510a2abd0b1a644bb0fdf9acc63625af6e25e72f","tid":212544,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宣傳宣傳者, 岩岩新到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正正經經打份工啦<br />\n<br />\n乞兒</blockquote><br />\n我只係業餘唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4437e22a23852d00a00c1c29055acf429f2c0fc7","tid":212544,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚難聽<br />\n<br />\n專心讀書<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁撚多明星夢"},{"pid":"91d7f5d4f